# Blush Meadow Rabbitry — Netlify Redirects
# This file fixes the duplicate content SEO issue.
# It ensures the .netlify.app subdomain always redirects
# to your real domain so Google only indexes one version.
#
# IMPORTANT: Replace "blushmeadowrabbitry.com" with your actual domain name.

https://blushmeadow.netlify.app/*   https://www.blushmeadowrabbitry.com/:splat   301!
http://www.blushmeadowrabbitry.com/*  https://www.blushmeadowrabbitry.com/:splat  301!
http://blushmeadowrabbitry.com/*      https://www.blushmeadowrabbitry.com/:splat  301!
